ingredientsDesc:
1. Tubes coated with GAM (Goat anti Mouse), 2x48 or 8x48 tubes
2. Tracer:125Iodine labeled T4 (HPLC grade) in phosphate buffer with bovine casein and azide (<0.1%) (l vial 21ml,111 kBq or 4 vials 21 ml, 4x111kBq)
3. Calibrators 0 in human serum, gentamycin and thymol(1 or 2 vial, lyophil.)

5. Anti-T4 (monoclonal) antibodies in phosphate buffer with bovine serum albumin and thymol (1 or 4 vials lyophil.)
6. Wash solution (TRIS-HCl), (1 or 4 vials, 10 ml)
7. Controls 1 or 2 in human serum with gentamycin and thymol (2 or 4 vials lyophil.)
